rms.model

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • rms.model.Resources

  • public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is meant to be used with the PRMS database. It is a model class for the Resources table in the database. Each resource is given a unique ID. Each ID represents a resource with name, description, room number, resource type id, location id, availability, super room designation, and capacity.
